<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .protected-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd 0%, #ffeaa7 100%);
            border: 2px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .lock-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #856404;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .session-details {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .content-section {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .test-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .test-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .test-link:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="protected-container">
        <div class="lock-icon">ðŸ”’</div>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p>This is a protected page that requires authentication. You have successfully accessed it!</p>
        
        <div class="session-details">
            <h3>Session Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Session Token:</strong> <code><%= sessionToken %></code></p>
            <p><strong>Access Time:</strong> <%= new Date().toISOString() %></p>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #28a745;">âœ… Authenticated</span></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-section">
            <h3>Protected Content</h3>
            <p>This content is only visible to authenticated users. It demonstrates that cookie-based authentication is working correctly for the Printeer CLI testing.</p>
            
            <ul>
                <li>Session validation: âœ… Passed</li>
                <li>Cookie authentication: âœ… Working</li>
                <li>Protected route access: âœ… Granted</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="test-links">
            <h4>Additional Tests:</h4>
            <a href="/debug/cookies" class="test-link">View All Cookies</a>
            <a href="/debug/headers" class="test-link">View Headers</a>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="test-link">Login Again</a>
        </div>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; color: #856404; font-style: italic;">
            This page confirms that authentication and session management are working correctly.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>